<plot>A beautiful angelic voice touches our hearts. It is the voice of Lacey, singing to her beloved Mark. Their world is perfect, their love washing away all worries. Then, Lacey wakes up from her dream. She is back to being her gawky self, an office worker watching handsome Mark from a distance. Lacey is the shyest girl around, and she has never spoken to the man of her dreams. Hell, he does not even know she exists. But the powers of her fantasies are too strong, and maybe today they will break out.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?100522</url></doc>
